-- National Bank of Kuwait appoints Nasser al-Sayer chairman
-- By Azza Al Arabi
-- Tue Aug 19, 2014 06:57AM EDT
-- None



DUBAI, Aug 19 (Reuters) - National Bank of Kuwait <NBKK.KW>, the Gulf Arab state's largest commercial lender, appointed Nasser Abdullah al-Sayer as its new chairman, the bank said on Tuesday.

Sayer previously served as deputy chairman of the bank's board of directors.